color=#000000><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: inherit; mso-hansi-font-family: inherit; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">第一，未按《企业会计准则第</SPAN><SPAN 
